<includeonly>{{Category/sidebox-header | category={{{category|}}} | label={{{label|}}} }}
{{Category/display-rows | category={{{category|}}} | page={{{page|{{FULLPAGENAME}}}}} }}
{{Category/sidebox-footer | category={{{category|}}} | page={{{page|{{FULLPAGENAME}}}}} | subobjects={{{subobjects|yes}}} | backlinks={{{backlinks|{{{subobjects|yes}}}}}} }}</includeonly><noinclude>
Dynamic-discovery sidebox display: composes `sidebox-header`,
`display-rows`, and `sidebox-footer` into a floating sidebar layout.
See `Category/table` for the broader composition pattern — this
template is identical apart from the outer chrome.

Parameters:
* category   - The category name. Required.
* label      - Optional display label.
* page       - Target page for the dynamic row lookup. Defaults to
               {{FULLPAGENAME}}.
* subobjects - "no" to suppress the nested subobjects block.
* backlinks  - "no" to suppress the backlinks row.
</noinclude>
